**Innkeeper** | Townsfolk Power | Archived
__Basics__
Each night, the Innkeeper may invite a guest to the inn.
__Details__
Each night, the Innkeeper may add a player to the inn. The Innkeeper can anonymously talk to all the guests of the inn. Adding a guest is immediate effect.
During each day, the Innkeeper may choose to clear the inn. Clearing the inn removes all guests and messages and is an end effect.
If the Innkeeper dies the inn is cleared.
